column2: SELECT s.stable_id as case_id, m.* FROM sample_list sl , sample_list_list sll , sample s , genetic_profile gp , mutation m where sl.stable_id = # and sl.list_id = sll.list_id and s.internal_id = sll.sample_id and gp.stable_id = # and m.sample_id = s.internal_id and m.genetic_profile_id = gp.genetic_profile_id
